  "description": {
    "zh": "我们继续，你脸上的表情已经写着“兴奋”了，对吧？我们还没看完所有的冲锋枪呢，记得吗？\n\n这对你来说是小菜一碟，更现代的武器，其中一些在护甲穿透方面也好得多，我当然甚至会给你一些备用弹药，一切都是为了你，捍卫者！`但是嘿，我可不是随便到处免费发放顶级子弹的！你有工作要做，我期望完美地完成，明白吗？就当是一项投资。\n\n当我说你不会让我失望时，我真的很自信，确保这句话成立。明白吗？",
    "en": "Let's continue, that look on your face already screams \"Excitement\", am I right? We haven't gone through all the submachineguns yet, remember?\n\nThis will be a cakewalk for you, more modern weaponry, some of them are also much better at armor penetration, I'll even give you some spare ammunition of course, everything for you champion!`But hey I don't just go around throwing top-tier bullets around for free! You have work to do, and I expect it to be done flawlessly, got it? Consider it an investment.\n\nI'm feeling really confident here when I say you won't disappoint me, make sure this statement stays true. Got it?"
  },
